Paper: hep-th/9208079

Date: 1992-08-31

Title: Free Field Representation of Quantum Affine Algebra U_q(\hat{sl}_2)

Authors: A. Matsuo

Comments: 11 pages

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B308 (1993) 260-265

A Fock representation of the quantum affine algebra $U_q(\widehat{\sl}_2)$ isconstructed by three bosonic fields for an arbitrary level with the help of theDrinfeld realization.